 16→/**
 17→ * Parse an email address.
 18→ *
 19→ * This class currently doesn't support internationalized domain names (RFC 5891) or non-ASCII local parts (RFC 6532).
 20→ *
 21→ * From RFC 5321:
 22→ * ```
 23→ * Mailbox                 = Local-part "@" ( Domain / address-literal )
 24→ *
 25→ * Local-part              = Dot-string / Quoted-string
 26→ * Dot-string              = Atom *("."  Atom)
 27→ * Quoted-string           = DQUOTE *QcontentSMTP DQUOTE
 28→ * QcontentSMTP            = qtextSMTP / quoted-pairSMTP
 29→ * qtextSMTP               = %d32-33 / %d35-91 / %d93-126
 30→ * quoted-pairSMTP         = %d92 %d32-126
 31→ *
 32→ * Domain                  - see DomainParser
 33→ * address-literal         - We intentionally don't support address literals
 34→ * ```
 35→ */
